hor TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.344</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:356\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">356</biblScope> </bibl>; by Iris to Athena, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:423\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.423</biblScope> </bibl>; by Hera to Artemis, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:481\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.481</biblScope> </bibl>: of the maids in the house of Odysseus, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:18:338\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.338</biblScope></bibl>, al.: later, in a coarse sense, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg004.perseus-grc1:1402\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ V.\">V.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1402</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἡ ῥαψῳδὸς κ.</foreign>, of the Sphinx, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg004.perseus-grc1:391\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OT\">OT</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">391</biblScope></bibl>, cf.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg008:236\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">236</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.); of men, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"